SUMMARY:“MAGIC VS SCIENCE\,” SEPT. 6 - 27
DESCRIPTION:Chicago’s brand new Stars & Garters\, 3914 N Clark St\, presents Magic VS Science produced by Thom Britton\, now playing every Saturday at 7 p.m. in the Rouge Room\, Sept. 6 -27 \n  \nThom Britton (Freakshow & Tell) is a fire-wielding science savant. Nolan Webster is Chicago’s most mysterious person—an enigmatic rogue who manipulates minds\, bends perception and reveals truths no one dares to speak aloud. Together\, they bring you an unforgettable night where science collides with the unexplained. \n  \nThis show is intended for audiences 21+. Tickets are $33.99 and available at StarsandGarters.club or by calling the box office at (773) 242-9929.
URL:https://evanstonmade.org/event/magic-vs-science-sept-6-27/2026-03-21/
LOCATION:Stars & Garters\, 3914 N. Clark St.\, Chicago\, IL\, 60613\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://evanstonmade.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/MVS11X17.jpg
END:VEVENT
