SUMMARY:STARS & GARTERS AFTER DARK
DESCRIPTION:Chicago’s brand new Stars & Garters\, 3914 N Clark St\, presents Stars & Garters After Dark\, every Thursday at 7 p.m. in the Rouge Room. \n  \nAudiences are invited to enjoy a wonderful evening of live Jazz with the Steve Knight Duo and a magical interlude by John Sturk\, David Jeselski or friends. The Stars & Garters mixologists will create delicious cocktails available at the bar and during the performance.  \nThis show is intended for audiences 21+. Tickets are $30 and are available at StarsandGarters.club or by calling the box office at (773) 242-9929.
URL:https://evanstonmade.org/event/stars-garters-after-dark/2026-03-26/
